## Test

```sh
cargo build --release
cargo test
```

## Architecture

This project uses:
- [xll-rs](https://crates.io/crates/xll-rs) - XLL runtime
- [xllgen](https://crates.io/crates/xllgen) - Function registration macros
- [xll-utils](https://crates.io/crates/xll-utils) - Export verification
